Definition: any of a family of glassy minerals analogous to feldspar containing hydrated aluminum silicates of calcium or sodium or potassium
Example: formed in cavities in lava flows and in plutonic rocks
Synonyms: mineral, water_softener, any, of, a, family, glassy, minerals, analogous, to, feldspar, containing, hydrated, aluminum, silicates, calcium, or, sodium, potassium, formed, in, cavities, lava, flows, and, plutonic, rocks
Category: noun.substance
